channel.title: Missing Publishers on IATI Registry
channel.description:
We've spotted a data issue where US-GOV-11 (and other similar umbrella publishers) are not listed in the Registry.
We've put more details [here](https://github.com/devinit/D-Portal/issues/516) as we don't know where specifically to raise this.
